description: Inspired by the classic Belgian street treat, delicious and authentic pommes frites are here to satisfy your hunger! Bruges Brother is bringing you "hand-forged frites" made-to-order, and topped with their delicious sauces. Along with their entrees, like fish & chips, roquefort steak, wild mushroom poutine, and more, you'll be sure to find something to love from Bruges Brothers!
name: Bruges Brothers
